30+ teams. 750+ athletes. Notable: men's and women's hockey (ACCHL champs), Esports (Big South Overwatch champs), Men's Golf (NCCGA national finalists), field hockey.

### Game-day language
"Get loud, get proud, get hyped." "Go Panthers!" "Roaring energy." "Panther Hype Night." "Celebration Plaza."

### Fight Song handling
HPU has a Fight Song with "Choose to be Extraordinary®" as the rallying line and a "Go HPU!" + Panther Shout closer ("H-I-G-H P-O-I-N-T, High Point Panthers"). The full lyrics are HPU's property. Reference by name and quote short phrases, don't reproduce all of it.

