14 meals per week default. Three components: Global Dining (weekly swipes), Magic Meal Dining (7 per semester at specialty spots), Dining Dollars (cash-equivalent supplement).

### Global Dining venues (weekly swipes)
Farmers Market (R.G. Wanek). The Café (Slane). Silver Line Diner and Market. The Village Grille.

