Jamba Juice. The Market @Wanek and @Yadkin. Great Day Bakery. Sunshine Café. The Brunch Place. Village Juice & Kitchen. Purple Pie ("extraordinary pizza"). Butterfly Café. The Point. Barberitos. Subway. Chick-fil-A. Slane Center Starbucks. Cottrell Starbucks.

### Fine Dining (by reservation, business professional dress)
1924 PRIME. Alo (in the Jana and Ken Kahn Hotel). Kazoku (hibachi in Panther Commons; "Kazoku" means family in Japanese).

### Dining context
20+ dining options on campus. 99% HPU Dining satisfaction rate (highest in nation). Princeton Review Top 20 Best Campus Food. Princeton Review #18 Best Campus Food specifically. Mobile Ordering app. Weekly food truck events. Cuisine & Culture Series at 1924 PRIME.

