## Honor Code

Signed by every student during Welcome Week. The Honor Code is on a 6-by-8-foot document students physically sign. HPU's property. Reference by name, quote short lines, don't reproduce in full.

Key line for quotation: "I will strive to be extraordinary in my academic studies and all other personal and professional pursuits."

The Honor Code's named commitments: refrain from conduct unbecoming of an HPU student; abstain from cheating; abstain from collusion; abstain from plagiarism; confront violations; report violations; civility pledge.

